        "reaction_type": "裂解反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Cracking reaction",
        "description": "在H-MFI型沸石催化剂上，使用环辛烷作为溶剂，对聚丙烯进行形状选择性裂解。反应在663-693K下进行1小时，将聚丙烯选择性转化为C3-27脂肪族和单环芳香族化合物（相当于液化石油气、石脑油、煤油、喷气燃料和柴油），同时回收大部分环辛烷溶剂。",
        "text_snippet": "With an H-MFI type zeolite catalyst combined with cyclooctane as the solvent, polypropylene was selectively converted without cyclooctane reactivity. In a typical case, 84% of polypropylene was converted into C3-27 aliphatic and monocyclic aromatic compounds (equivalent to liquid petroleum gas, naphtha, kerosene, jet and diesel) with 79% selectivity, while 95% of cyclooctane was recovered.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Cracking reaction"
      }
    ]
  },
